was one of sadness:

17
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:21,790
a degenerate king, sickly infantes,

18
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:25,749
idiots, dwarfs, cripples,

19
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,037
a handful of clownish freaks
dressed up as princes,

20
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:31,840
whose function it was
to laugh at themselves...

21
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:35,197
and to amuse a cast
that lived outside the law,

22
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:39,718
in the meshes of etiquette,
plots and lies,

23
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:43,589
bound by the confessional and remorse,

24
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:48,118
