- Next, we find Ferdinand arriving in...
- Toulon.

818
01:14:06,440 --> 01:14:09,398
He strolls along the waterfront.
He is staying...

819
01:14:09,640 --> 01:14:11,073
at the Little Palace Hotel.

820
