around the thing they designate

826
01:14:28,080 --> 01:14:30,036
even if it is degraded in everyday life.

827
01:14:30,280 --> 01:14:32,271
Words retain only what is pure.

828
01:14:46,120 --> 01:14:51,114
In Viet Nam, the Da Nang base,
a major US stronghold,

829
01:14:51,360 --> 01:14:52,998
was raided by the Viet Cong.

830
01:14:53,240 --> 01:14:55,879
7 planes were destroyed
on the ground.

831
01:14:56,120 --> 01:14:57,235
In the jungle,

832
01:14:57,480 --> 01:15:02,554
US soldiers fought side by side for the
first time with South Vietnamese forces...

833
